                <lb n="1"/>
                <persName type="divine" ref="#vanammon"><name nymRef="Vanammon">Uanammoni</name> <addName nymRef="Augustus"><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan></addName></persName> <w lemma="sacer"><expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>rum</ex></expan></w> 
                <lb n="2"/><persName type="attested"><name nymRef="Aurelius">Aurelius</name> <name nymRef="Varixen">Uarixen</name></persName> <w lemma="ordinarius"><expan><abbr>ordin</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan></w> 
                <lb n="3"/><w lemma="qui">qui</w> <w lemma="ex">ex</w> <w lemma="fortis">fortia</w> <w lemma="et">et</w> <w lemma="suffragium"><expan><abbr>suff</abbr><ex>ragio</ex></expan></w> <w lemma="uexillatio"><expan><abbr>uex</abbr><ex>illationi</ex></expan></w> 
                <lb n="4"/><w lemma="proficio"><expan><abbr>profec</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan></w> <w lemma="ex">ex</w> <w lemma="uotum">uoto</w> 
                <lb n="5"/><w lemma="ab">a</w> <w lemma="solum">solo</w> <w lemma="exstruo">extruxit</w> <w lemma="libens"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan></w> <w lemma="animus"><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nimo</ex></expan></w>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="translation" source="#rebuffat1990" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>Consacré à Vanammon Auguste. Aurelius Varixen, (centurion) ordinaire, qui a par son courage et son action servi la vexillatio, a  accompli son voeu de bon coeur
                    en construisant ce temple intégralement.</p> 
            </div>
            <div type="translation" resp="#cmr" xml:lang="en">
                <p>Sacred to Vanammon Augustus: Aurelius Varixen, ordinarius, who, from his strength and judgement (?) commanded the company, 
                    erected <supplied reason="subaudible">the monument</supplied> from the ground up, accomplishing his vow willingly</p></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p/>
            </div>
